txt.en: You have recovered a stolen gem from one of the Orkish miners in Glimmerdeep mine. Are there more such gems to be claimed?

'I see these gems, while tarnished, could be quite valuable in the hands of a skilled gem-cutter.\n\n'I will give the Zhélruka only one gem, and tell them there is more where this came from in the Glimmerdeep.'
Orc-kind from have taken over the Glimmerdeep and work to mine its wealth.
You should bring the gems to Agátur in Skarháld.
You should collect tarnished gems from the Orc-kind in Glimmerdeep mine.
